description	"Clone Trooper EMP Grenade Specialist Unit

^2Weaponry:
- DC-17 Clone Pistol (2)
- DC-15S Carbine (3)
- 3 EMP Grenades

^6Inventory:
- Portable Shield

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (2) ^3[CS1]

Clone troopers were identical, genetically-modified soldiers bred and trained to serve in the Republic's army during the conflict that came to be known as the Clone Wars.
The Reverse Pulse Polarity grenade was a specialized weapon that emitted a reversing polarity pulse wave upon detonation that would literally crush droids caught within the blast radius of the grenade by overloading their systems."